  "texts": [
    "Finally, to generate the labels (questionanswer pairs) of our gold-standard dataset, we create mappings between the questions from Section Question collection and the gold-standard answers from Section Gold-standard answer extraction.",
    "We achieve this by considering the query groups in Table 1.",
    "For each query group, we identify a group of words in the gold-standard answers that are most likely to provide the information inquired by that query group.",
    "To compile this group of words, we engage in meticulous manual exploration, reading sentences containing IDU keywords.",
    "Depending on the kind of information we are interested in (reflected by the query groups), these words can be either the keywords in Table 2 or the words (Supplementary Table 1) that co-occur with the keywords and can help convey the information inquired by the user."
  ],
